animes.name: SF-A2 miki (Mikina Freesis, Mickina Olliba)
animes.full_desc:
SF-A2 miki  (SF-A2 開発コード miki)
SF-A2 codename miki, is a Japanese VOCALOID developed and distributed by AH-Software Co. Ltd., and was released in December 2009 for the VOCALOID2 engine. Her voice is provided by the Japanese female singer, Miki Furukawa.


Alternative names/personalities:
Aku no Musume: Mikina Freesis (ミキナ=フリージス)
Venomania-kou no Kyouki: Mickina Olliba
